    <entry>
      <title>Docker常用命令总结</title>
      <link href="/2026/03/12/post/"/>
      <url>/2026/03/12/post/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Docker-常用命令关系图"><a href="#Docker-常用命令关系图" class="headerlink" title="Docker 常用命令关系图"></a>Docker 常用命令关系图</h2><div align="center">    <img src="/assert/2026-03-12.png" alt="Docker 常用命令关系图" style="max-width: 920px; width: 100%; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 18px #00000018; margin: 20px 0 28px 0;" /></div><p>从使用顺序看，最常见的链路就是：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Dockerfile -&gt; docker build -&gt; image -&gt; docker run -&gt; container</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>再补四组高频动作就够了：</p><ul><li><strong>镜像仓库</strong>：<code>docker pull</code>、<code>docker push</code></li><li><strong>镜像管理</strong>：<code>docker images</code>、<code>docker rmi</code></li><li><strong>容器管理</strong>：<code>docker ps</code>、<code>docker stop</code>、<code>docker start</code>、<code>docker rm</code></li><li><strong>数据挂载</strong>：<code>volume</code> 更适合持久化，<code>bind mount</code> 更适合开发联调</li></ul><h2 id="Dockerfile-是做什么的"><a href="#Dockerfile-是做什么的" class="headerlink" title="Dockerfile 是做什么的"></a>Dockerfile 是做什么的</h2><p><code>Dockerfile</code> 就是镜像的构建说明书，核心流程通常只有这几步：</p><ul><li>选基础镜像：<code>FROM</code></li><li>拷贝代码：<code>COPY</code></li><li>安装依赖：<code>RUN</code></li><li>暴露端口：<code>EXPOSE</code></li><li>指定启动命令：<code>CMD</code></li></ul><p>一个最常见的 Node 项目示例：</p><figure class="highlight dockerfile"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">FROM</span> node:<span class="number">20</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">WORKDIR</span><span class="language-bash"> /app</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">COPY</span><span class="language-bash"> package*.json ./</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">RUN</span><span class="language-bash"> npm install</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">COPY</span><span class="language-bash"> . .</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">EXPOSE</span> <span class="number">3000</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">CMD</span><span class="language-bash"> [<span class="string">&quot;npm&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;run&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;dev&quot;</span>]</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>构建镜像：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker build -t myapp:1.0 .</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>运行容器：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker run -d --name myapp -p 3000:3000 myapp:1.0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Docker-Compose-是做什么的"><a href="#Docker-Compose-是做什么的" class="headerlink" title="Docker Compose 是做什么的"></a>Docker Compose 是做什么的</h2><p>如果项目不止一个容器，比如 <code>web + mysql</code>，一个个 <code>docker run</code> 会很乱，这时更适合用 <code>docker compose</code> 统一管理。</p><p>最常见的 <code>compose.yml</code> 结构包括：</p><ul><li><code>services</code>：定义有哪些服务</li><li><code>ports</code>：端口映射</li><li><code>volumes</code>：数据卷</li><li><code>environment</code>：环境变量</li><li><code>depends_on</code>：启动依赖</li></ul><p>例如：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">services:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">web:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">image:</span> <span class="string">node:20</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">container_name:</span> <span class="string">webapp</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">working_dir:</span> <span class="string">/app</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">volumes:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">/home/user/project:/app</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">ports:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">&quot;3000:3000&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">command:</span> <span class="string">npm</span> <span class="string">run</span> <span class="string">dev</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">depends_on:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">db</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">db:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">image:</span> <span class="string">mysql:8</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">container_name:</span> <span class="string">mysql8</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">environment:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD:</span> <span class="number">123456</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">MYSQL_DATABASE:</span> <span class="string">app</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">ports:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">&quot;3306:3306&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">volumes:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">mysql_data:/var/lib/mysql</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">volumes:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">mysql_data:</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>常用命令：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker compose up -d</span><br><span class="line">docker compose ps</span><br><span class="line">docker compose logs -f</span><br><span class="line">docker compose down</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="挂载怎么选"><a href="#挂载怎么选" class="headerlink" title="挂载怎么选"></a>挂载怎么选</h2><p>原则很简单：</p><ul><li><strong>要持久化业务数据</strong>，选 <code>volume</code></li><li><strong>要把宿主机目录直接映射进容器</strong>，选 <code>bind mount</code></li><li><strong>命令写法上</strong>，直接记 <code>-v</code> 就够用</li></ul><h3 id="1-Volume"><a href="#1-Volume" class="headerlink" title="1. Volume"></a>1. Volume</h3><p>适合数据库、缓存、上传文件这类需要长期保留的数据。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker volume create mydata</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">docker run -d \</span><br><span class="line">  --name mynginx \</span><br><span class="line">  -v mydata:/usr/share/nginx/html \</span><br><span class="line">  nginx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>常用配套命令：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker volume <span class="built_in">ls</span></span><br><span class="line">docker volume inspect mydata</span><br><span class="line">docker volume <span class="built_in">rm</span> mydata</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-Bind-Mount"><a href="#2-Bind-Mount" class="headerlink" title="2. Bind Mount"></a>2. Bind Mount</h3><p>适合本地开发，把源码或配置直接挂进容器，宿主机改完文件，容器里会同步看到。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker run -d \</span><br><span class="line">  --name mynginx2 \</span><br><span class="line">  -v /home/user/nginx-html:/usr/share/nginx/html \</span><br><span class="line">  -p 8080:80 \</span><br><span class="line">  nginx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这也是平时最常见的写法。</p><h2 id="常用命令"><a href="#常用命令" class="headerlink" title="常用命令"></a>常用命令</h2><h3 id="镜像"><a href="#镜像" class="headerlink" title="镜像"></a>镜像</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker pull nginx</span><br><span class="line">docker images</span><br><span class="line">docker build -t myapp:1.0 .</span><br><span class="line">docker rmi nginx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="容器"><a href="#容器" class="headerlink" title="容器"></a>容器</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker run -d --name mynginx -p 8080:80 nginx</span><br><span class="line">docker ps</span><br><span class="line">docker ps -a</span><br><span class="line">docker stop mynginx</span><br><span class="line">docker start mynginx</span><br><span class="line">docker <span class="built_in">rm</span> -f mynginx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="进入容器与排查"><a href="#进入容器与排查" class="headerlink" title="进入容器与排查"></a>进入容器与排查</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker <span class="built_in">exec</span> -it mynginx sh</span><br><span class="line">docker logs -f mynginx</span><br><span class="line">docker inspect mynginx</span><br><span class="line">docker stats</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="网络与清理"><a href="#网络与清理" class="headerlink" title="网络与清理"></a>网络与清理</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker network <span class="built_in">ls</span></span><br><span class="line">docker network create mynet</span><br><span class="line">docker system prune</span><br><span class="line">docker volume prune</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> docker </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>乐观锁和悲观锁</title>
      <link href="/2026/03/10/post/"/>
      <url>/2026/03/10/post/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>并发修改同一条数据时，最常见的问题就是“丢失更新”。这也是乐观锁和悲观锁存在的核心原因。</p><blockquote><p>悲观锁是“先锁再改”，乐观锁是“提交时校验再改”。</p></blockquote><hr><p>比如账户余额是 <code>100</code>，两个请求同时扣款：</p><ul><li>请求1扣 <code>20</code></li><li>请求2扣 <code>30</code></li></ul><p>如果都先读到旧值 <code>100</code>，最后结果可能变成 <code>70</code>，而正确结果应该是 <code>50</code>。</p><p>为了解决这个问题，常见方案只有两类：</p><ul><li><strong>悲观锁</strong>：先锁住，再修改</li><li><strong>乐观锁</strong>：先不锁，提交时检查数据有没有被别人改过</li></ul><hr><h2 id="悲观锁"><a href="#悲观锁" class="headerlink" title="悲观锁"></a>悲观锁</h2><p>悲观锁假设冲突经常发生，所以直接把记录锁住。</p><p>常见写法：</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> balance</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="keyword">user</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> id <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> <span class="keyword">update</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>拿到锁的事务先执行，其他事务要等它提交后才能继续。优点是结果稳定、控制强；缺点是会阻塞，吞吐量低，还有死锁风险。</p><p>适合场景：</p><ul><li>写多读少</li><li>热点数据竞争激烈</li><li>数据不能出错，且可以接受等待</li></ul><hr><h2 id="乐观锁"><a href="#乐观锁" class="headerlink" title="乐观锁"></a>乐观锁</h2><p>乐观锁假设大多数时候不会冲突，所以不提前加锁，而是在更新时带上条件。</p><p>最常见的是 <code>version</code> 方案：</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">update</span> <span class="keyword">user</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">set</span> balance <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">80</span>, version <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> id <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">1</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> version <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>只有当数据库里的 <code>version</code> 还是旧值时，这次更新才会成功；如果别人已经改过，这条 SQL 会影响 <code>0</code> 行，业务层再决定是否重试。</p><p>它的关键在于：<code>update ... where ...</code> 是数据库原子操作，判断和更新一次完成，所以不会发生错误覆盖。</p><p>适合场景：</p><ul><li>读多写少</li><li>冲突概率低</li><li>可以接受失败后重试</li><li>更关注并发性能</li></ul><hr><h2 id="两者区别"><a href="#两者区别" class="headerlink" title="两者区别"></a>两者区别</h2><table><thead><tr><th>维度</th><th>乐观锁</th><th>悲观锁</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>思路</td><td>提交时检查</td><td>修改前先加锁</td></tr><tr><td>是否阻塞</td><td>通常不阻塞</td><td>会阻塞</td></tr><tr><td>并发性能</td><td>高</td><td>较低</td></tr><tr><td>冲突处理</td><td>失败或重试</td><td>等待</td></tr><tr><td>常见实现</td><td><code>version</code>、旧值判断</td><td><code>for update</code></td></tr></tbody></table><hr><h2 id="实际怎么选"><a href="#实际怎么选" class="headerlink" title="实际怎么选"></a>实际怎么选</h2><p>可以直接按这个原则判断：</p><ul><li><strong>读多写少、普通 CRUD</strong>：优先乐观锁</li><li><strong>冲突频繁、热点竞争强</strong>：优先悲观锁</li><li><strong>库存扣减这类固定规则更新</strong>：优先原子条件更新</li></ul><p>库存场景里也常见这种写法：</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">update</span> product</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">set</span> stock <span class="operator">=</span> stock <span class="operator">-</span> <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">where</span> id <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">1</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> stock <span class="operator">&gt;</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这不一定是标准 <code>version</code> 乐观锁，但本质也是并发控制，因为它把“校验”和“扣减”合成了一条原子 SQL。</p><hr><h2 id="一句话总结"><a href="#一句话总结" class="headerlink" title="一句话总结"></a>一句话总结</h2><ul><li><strong>悲观锁</strong>：我先锁住，别人别动</li><li><strong>乐观锁</strong>：你们先改，提交时我再检查</li></ul><p>如果你用的是 MyBatis-Plus，工程上通常更推荐直接用 <code>@Version</code> 做标准乐观锁。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> Java开发 </tag>
            
            <tag> Mybatis </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
